<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
<title>WWA - Social Friction</title>
<style>
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { background: #0a0a0a; color: #e0e0e0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; padding: 1.25rem; min-height: 100vh; }
.title-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #555; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.shoot-title { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: #f0f0f0; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.meta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.meta-pill { font-size: 11px; color: #888; background: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius: 99px; padding: 4px 10px; }
.meta-pill span { color: #c8ff00; }
.prog-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.prog-row p { font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
.prog-row strong { font-size: 12px; color: #f0f0f0; }
.progress-bar { height: 4px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.progress-fill { height: 100%; background: #c8ff00; border-radius: 99px; transition: width 0.3s ease; }
.section-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #555; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
.shot { background: #141414; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 1px solid #1e1e1e; overflow: hidden; }
.shot.done { opacity: 0.4; }
.shot.done .shot-title { text-decoration: line-through; color: #555; }
.shot-header { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; padding: 14px; cursor: pointer; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
.cb { width: 24px; height: 24px; min-width: 24px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1.5px solid #333; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: transparent; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
.shot.done .cb, .complete-row.done .cb { background: #c8ff00; border-color: #c8ff00; }
.check-icon { width: 13px; height: 13px; stroke: #000; stroke-width: 2.5; fill: none; display: none; }
.shot.done .check-icon, .complete-row.done .check-icon { display: block; }
.shot-body { flex: 1; }
.shot-num { font-size: 10px; color: #555; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 3px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.shot-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #e0e0e0; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.3; }
.shot-detail { font-size: 13px; color: #666; line-height: 1.55; }
.script-section { border-top: 1px solid #1e1e1e; padding: 12px 14px 14px 52px; }
.script-label { font-size: 9px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c8ff00; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
.script-lines { font-size: 13px; color: #777; line-height: 1.9; font-style: italic; }
.script-lines .key { color: #bbb; font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; }
.tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 99px; margin-right: 4px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.tag-training { background: #1a2a1a; color: #4caf50; border: 1px solid #2a3a2a; }
.tag-atelier { background: #1a1a2a; color: #7c8fff; border: 1px solid #2a2a3a; }
.tag-music { background: #2a1a2a; color: #ce7cff; border: 1px solid #3a2a3a; }
.tag-travel { background: #2a1f1a; color: #ff9c5c; border: 1px solid #3a2f2a; }
.divider { height: 1px; background: #1a1a1a; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
.note-box { background: #111; border-left: 2px solid #c8ff00; border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0; padding: 12px 14px; margin-top: 1rem; }
.note-box p { font-size: 13px; color: #777; line-height: 1.65; }
.note-box strong { color: #c8ff00; }
.reset-btn { width: 100%; margin-top: 1.25rem; padding: 14px; background: #141414; border: 1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius: 12px; color: #555; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
.complete-section { margin-top: 2rem; background: #141414; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #1e1e1e; padding: 14px; }
.complete-title { font-size: 10px; color: #555; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.complete-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e1e; cursor: pointer; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
.complete-row:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
.complete-row.done .complete-label { color: #555; text-decoration: line-through; }
.complete-label { font-size: 14px; color: #bbb; flex: 1; }
.date-label { font-size: 11px; color: #555; margin: 12px 0 6px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
.date-input { width: 100%; background: #0f0f0f; border: 1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius: 8px; color: #bbb; font-size: 14px; padding: 10px 12px; font-family: inherit; outline: none; }
.legend { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.legend-label { font-size: 10px; color: #555; width: 100%; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.vo-box { background: #0f0f0f; border: 1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.vo-title { font-size: 10px; color: #c8ff00; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.vo-line { font-size: 13px; color: #888; line-height: 2; font-style: italic; }
.vo-line .key { color: #ddd; font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="title-label">WWA · Archive Edit</div>
<div class="shoot-title">Social Friction</div>

<div class="meta-row">
  <div class="meta-pill">Format: <span>Voiceover + Text Overlay</span></div>
  <div class="meta-pill">Footage: <span>Archive</span></div>
  <div class="meta-pill">Operator: <span>Henry</span></div>
</div>

<div class="prog-row"><p>Progress</p><strong id="prog-text">0 / 12</strong></div>
<div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="prog-fill" style="width:0%"></div></div>

<div class="section-label">Footage Key</div>
<div class="legend">
  <div class="legend-label">Archive categories</div>
  <span class="tag tag-training">Training</span>
  <span class="tag tag-atelier">WWA Atelier</span>
  <span class="tag tag-music">Music</span>
  <span class="tag tag-travel">Travel</span>
</div>

<div class="section-label">Full Voiceover Script</div>
<div class="vo-box">
  <div class="vo-title">Read in full before pulling clips</div>
  <div class="vo-line">
    <span class="key">What takes most people years to figure out only took me months.</span><br>
    <span class="key">Now you're gonna get it in seconds.</span><br><br>
    If nobody around you feels the pressure you feel — you're operating at a level they're not built for.<br>
    If nobody thinks your standards are extreme — they're not high enough.<br>
    If nobody thinks what you're doing is realistic — your vision is just bigger than their frame of reference.<br>
    If someone tries to talk you out of it — it's because your commitment makes them uncomfortable.<br>
    That's a compliment.<br>
    When they say you're obsessed — it means they've never wanted anything bad enough to understand.<br>
    And the ones who go quiet when you level up?<br>
    They're not ignoring you.<br>
    They're recalibrating.<br><br>
    <span class="key">Social friction is not a sign you're doing something wrong.</span><br>
    <span class="key">It's proof you're doing something most people never will.</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>
<div class="section-label">Edit Sequence</div>

<div class="shot" data-id="s1">
  <div class="shot-header" onclick="toggle(this.parentElement)">
    <div class="cb"><svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 13 13"><polyline points="2,6.5 5.5,10 11,3"/></svg></div>
