  <div class="shot-header" onclick="toggle(this.parentElement)">
    <div class="cb"><svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 13 13"><polyline points="2,6.5 5.5,10 11,3"/></svg></div>
    <div class="shot-body">
      <div class="shot-num">Clip 9 · Close</div>
      <div class="shot-title">The full picture — wide, cinematic, brand-defining</div>
      <div class="shot-detail">The strongest piece of archive footage across any category. The close needs to feel like the whole world of WATERWORLD in one frame. Pull the best thing in the archive.</div>
      <div style="margin-top:8px"><span class="tag tag-training">Training</span><span class="tag tag-atelier">WWA Atelier</span><span class="tag tag-music">Music</span><span class="tag tag-travel">Travel</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="script-section">
    <div class="script-label">Voiceover</div>
    <div class="script-lines">Social friction is not a sign you're doing something wrong.<br><span class="key">It's proof you're doing something most people never will.</span></div>
  </div>
