      <div class="shot-title">Grade: desaturated, cooler tones — consistent across all archive footage</div>
      <div class="shot-detail">The four footage categories will have different original grades. Unify them all under the WWA palette. Crushed blacks, cooler midtones. The edit should feel like one world, not four different shoots.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

